{"tid":1007642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"應召妹無言！客點2小時服務　竟要她幫忙搬家","createTime":"2019-02-04T02:02:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T03:42:52.000Z","uid":85957,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9141f1af0fe53e7b057ec3c42735b949ae770d42","tid":1007642,"uid":85957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T02:02:16.000Z","msg":"應召妹到客人家準備服務時，沒想到客人根本不想啪啪啪，只是把她叫來幫忙搬家。<br />\n日本女網友「みゆな」在《推特》發文抱怨，問在做風俗業的同行小姐們，「除了我以外，有人被客人點了2小時服務叫到家裡，然後幫忙搬家的經驗嗎？」還說幸好有小貨車可以運送。<br />\n<br />\n同行的女網友紛紛述說自己的經驗「我有遇過點3小時服務然後要幫忙搬家的，結束後還剩一些時間還打掃跟吃飯」、「我也有遇過要打掃、洗碗、洗床單的」、「雖然沒有遇過要幫家的，不過有遇過腰受傷不能動，要我幫忙餵飯吃的」，有網友說明，找應召妹搬家其實很划算，找搬家公司根本貴翻了。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xDCwcJr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxDCwcJr.png&h=83dc68ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190203/1512755/?utm_campaign=twad_social_apple.realtimenews&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190203%2F1512755%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_apple.realtimenews%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToNOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=2da33728\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190203%2F1512755%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_apple.realtimenews%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=d2dc1972\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190203/1512755/?utm_campaign=twad_social_apple.realtimenews&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"6baed7a73110ded49423b6616385bb20b59b968f","tid":1007642,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T02:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/f